p: Sera from rhesus macaques was analyzed for 14 cytokines and chemokines by Luminex using established protocols for Old World primates. Evaluation of interferon alpha (IFNα), interferon gamma (IFNγ), IL-1 receptor antagonist (IL-1Ra), inflammatory protein 1-alpha (MIP-1α, CCL3) and beta MIP-1β (CCL4), perforin and interferon gamma-induced protein 10 (IP-10, CXCL10) were included in this assay.
